<@U0XCJ372R> a couple small things if you have these files available at home (in order of priority):
1. On the week view, can we make Tuesday, June 21 (that's "today" in the prototype) reflect the active minute count and activity icons we already are using for the today screen? So 45min and walking, spinning, Dx, and running
2. On the Dx Join screen, can we switch "back to today" to "back to activity"?
3. On the Dx Complete screen, can we switch "back to today" to "back to activity"?
Thank you!!!

<@U0260V1BX> <@U0HP6TFNX> If you have a moment, could you take a spin through the second prototype? I left the paper at work where I drew the interaction model for flowing between today/week view/past days, so let me know if I've built what we previously discussed. Thanks <https://invis.io/BF952CBZX>
